o_hundred_day_avg":451.721,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":550.0,"all_time_low":335.0,"long_business_summary":"Axtel Industries Limited manufactures, supplies, and sells process engineering equipment and turnkey systems for food processing and pharmaceutical industries in India and internationally. The company provides solids handling equipment, such as sack tip stations, bulk loaders, belt conveyors, screw feeders and conveyors, screw feeder with valves, dual tunnel diverter valves, Z-bucket elevators, cyclones, blowers, magnets, dump booth, reverse jet filters, and octabin and tote tilters. It also offers storage and discharge equipment comprising storage tanks, cone discharge, big bag handling systems, valves, knife gate and butterfly valves, bin activators, table feeders, bagging stations, liquified injection pressure tanks, intermediate bulk containers, and storage bins. In addition, the company provides sieving and straining/cleaning and grading equipment, including rotary and gyratory sifters, graders, screeners, destoners, zig zag classifiers, chocolate vibrosieve, and vacuum gravity separators; and size reduction equipment consists of hammer and universal mills, nibblers, lump breakers, cone and knife mills, shredders, and roller mills. Further, it offers mixing and blending process equipment, such as vertical single and twin shaft mixers, paste mixers, horizontal round and U-trough mixers, liquifiers, intensive mixers, and double cone blenders. Additionally, the company provides specialized process equipment, including steam sterilizers, molding line cooling tunnels, conveyor dryers, continuous fryers, chocolate depositors, cooling tunnels, temperors, entolator, shots forming machines, cheese presses, caramel slab formers, forming and portioning machines, vacuum band and cabinet dryers, khoa making machines, IBC/big bag filling machines, dewatering screw presses, horizontal wiped film evaporators, scraped surface heat exchangers, shell and tube heat exchangers, steaming tunnels, and dough kneaders. Axtel Industries Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Halol, India."}}